So called Memory Stick Thumb Drive Jump Drive Pen Drive Zip Drive, Gigastone USB 3.0 has an elegant, sturdy and top quality texture that makes it easy to handle and use. Gigastone USB 3.0 is also tested under strict quality standards, speed testing, endurance validation and repeatedly plug in & plug out to ensure durable quality.
